    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> It is a turn-based tower defense, where elemental dragons replace towers, and you can combine their powers into devastating combinations! Supported by traps, curses, and ghosts in your arsenal, plan your defense and defeat all the thieves to prove no human being can even touch YOUR treasure!  </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Destroy waves of enemies in various ways</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Big dragons have strong, simple abilities, while small elemental ones are great for interesting combos</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092000/extras/79d81f27504f697b36a06a71ff5cfe8a.poster.avif?t=1761944267\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092000/extras/79d81f27504f697b36a06a71ff5cfe8a.webm?t=1761944267\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >For example, the combination of water and electricity will shock the enemy</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>You have five elements to combine: fire, ice, poison, electricity, and water</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092000/extras/606ac8f648905bbf60666b3196b185cf.poster.avif?t=1761944267\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092000/extras/606ac8f648905bbf60666b3196b185cf.webm?t=1761944267\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Discover unique dragons</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Some dragons require a completely different approach to defense</i></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092000/extras/74e1fd141282d1ec5b938b86040bca5e.poster.avif?t=1761944267\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092000/extras/74e1fd141282d1ec5b938b86040bca5e.webm?t=1761944267\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Create your own dragon lair</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Change the lighting, decorations, banners, and interior colors</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092000/extras/7ff798660f77c32ccca43241ab579c3e.poster.avif?t=1761944267\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092000/extras/7ff798660f77c32ccca43241ab579c3e.webm?t=1761944267\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Raise Elemental Dragons:</i> Nurture and grow smaller elemental dragons on each level. Each elemental dragon brings unique abilities, ability recharge rate, incubation rate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092000/extras/b6ef4dfb30c53eec7cc487d2a653add6.avif?t=1761944267\" width=620 height=348 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Elemental Mastery:</i> Harness the power of fire, ice, water, poison, and electricity. Combine these elements to create devastating effects like steam,  electrocution, freezing, burning, epidemics, poisoning and explosions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092000/extras/9475d400108db561861ba4e7e99cbde8.avif?t=1761944267\" width=620 height=348 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Set Traps:</i> Strategically place traps to outsmart and defeat waves of enemies. Plan your moves carefully to maximize their effectiveness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Variety of Enemies:</i> Face off against a diverse array of foes, each with unique traits. Fast thieves, shield-bearers that block projectile damage, and more will challenge your tactical skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Puzzle and Strategy:</i> The game is designed as a turn-based puzzle where planning and strategy are key. While it's easy to complete levels with a one-star rating, achieving three stars requires careful thought and execution.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Why Play Treasure Protector?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  If you enjoy games that blend strategy, puzzle-solving and a bit of fantasy, Treasure Protector is for you. With its unique elemental combinations and strategic depth, it offers a rewarding challenge for those willing to master its mechanics.</p>",
